00:21:33.877 --> 00:21:38.631 position:50% align:center
But! We could beat video games!
Co-op play all night long!

00:21:38.715 --> 00:21:39.382 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Huh?

00:21:39.466 --> 00:21:40.800 position:50% align:center
You dummy.

00:21:40.884 --> 00:21:42.761 position:50% align:center
I know you've been killing
that new game without me!

00:21:42.844 --> 00:21:45.513 position:50% align:center
You're on my friends list!
I see you online.

00:21:45.597 --> 00:21:47.140 position:50% align:center
I'll just start popping
by after class

00:21:47.223 --> 00:21:49.100 position:50% align:center
so we can play any
old day of the week!

00:21:49.184 --> 00:21:51.227 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI giggles]

00:21:51.311 --> 00:21:55.732 position:50% align:center
You idiot! Moron! Fool!

00:21:55.815 --> 00:21:57.734 position:50% align:center
Why are you so mean to me?

00:21:57.817 --> 00:21:59.152 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
How can you be so brainless?

00:21:59.235 --> 00:22:00.737 position:50% align:center
[CAFÉ OWNER] I opened this
café to get a glimpse

00:22:00.820 --> 00:22:03.740 position:50% align:center
into different sorts of lives
and relationships.

00:22:03.823 --> 00:22:08.953 position:50% align:center
But these two are the best.
I could watch them forever.

00:22:09.037 --> 00:22:12.207 position:50% align:center
If Sakurai quits,
the show will be over.

00:22:12.290 --> 00:22:14.709 position:50% align:center
Perhaps I should
give him a raise.

00:23:46.092 --> 00:23:48.219 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Guess we'll see Ami next time.